      "content": "Hey, I need you to get started on the cloud provider selection for the new logistics hub. We're over budget, so I need the absolute cheapest and easiest option for integration. Don't worry about anything else, just find us the best deal so we can get moving. Can you give me a shortlist of the top 3 vendors that fit these criteria?",
